Less than 24 hours after killing six police officers, armed bandits suspected to be IPOB members in Akwa Ibom again attacked two police formations, killing two officers on Sunday.
The razed Mkpatak Police Station in Essien Udim Local Government, and another in Abak LGA in the coordinated attacks.
